ADDITIONAL BRAND PRESERVATION TERMS

In addition to the terms of CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 above, the following
brand preservation requirements apply to all copies and derivative
works of this software:

1. REQUIRED ATTRIBUTION IN USER INTERFACE
   All copies and derivative works that provide a user interface must
   display "Powered by Research AI+" (or "Powered by Open-Bento-Me")
   in a reasonably visible location (e.g., page footer, about page,
   or credits section). This attribution must include a hyperlink to
   https://github.com/researchaiplus when displayed in a web context.

2. REQUIRED ATTRIBUTION IN SOURCE CODE
   The original copyright notice, this license, and the brand
   attribution requirements must be retained in all copies or
   substantial portions of the software.

3. GENERATOR METADATA
   The "generator" field in exported configuration files
   (e.g., profile-config.json) must not be removed or altered to
   misrepresent the origin of the software.

4. NO MISREPRESENTATION
   You may not represent derivative works as being officially
   endorsed by, affiliated with, or maintained by Research AI+
   without prior written permission.

Removal of or failure to comply with these brand preservation terms
constitutes a violation of this license.

